"12:109:27" : {s: 12, a: 109, w: 27, r: "وقي", t: "ٱتَّقَوْا۟", l: "ٱتَّقَىٰ", lc: 166, tl: "ittaqaw", lb: "কোনো কিছুর ব্যাপারে অত্যন্ত সচেতন থাকা, আল্লাহর প্রতি সচেতন থাকা",e: "fear Allah", b: "সচেতন হও (আল্লাহর প্রতি)", i: "(mereka) bertakwa", f: 9, rm: "to protect, save, preserve, ward off, guard against evil and calamity, be secure, take as a shield, regard the duty. muttaqii - one who guard against evil and against that which harms and injures and is regardful of his duty towards human beings and God.", ag: "فعل ماض صيغة ٨ وضمير متصل ", eg: "Verb Perfect 8th form and Pronoun suffix ", tag: "V", pos: "V", att: "PERF", qual: "(VIII)", deg: "3", gen: "M", num: "P", mood: "", lu: "ٱتَّقَىٰ"},
